Copying and Disclaimers

    @{fg  shine}Picticon@{fg  text}  was thrown together in a few days using  bits
and  pieces of @{"Iconian" link "Iconian" 0}.  If you haven't gotten a copy of Iconian,
 find one.  It is the number one OS3.x icon editor you can get (IMHO).

    Since  @{fg  highlight}Picticon@{fg  text}  is a patchwork program that's  held
together  by spaghetti sauce, many bugs will probably show up.  I will
honestly claim that I can get consistent, satisfactory results at this
time.   If  you do run across any, please let me know.  
SEE:   @{"Bugs"  link  "Bugs"  0}  @{"Registering  a  complaint"  LINK "Registering a complaint"}

